file.name: library-api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Library API
  description: Library API
  version: 0.1.0
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:8080'
paths:
  /books:
    get:
      tags:
        - books
      summary: Find books by author
      operationId: findBooksByAuthor
      responses:
        '200':
          description: List of found books is returned
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Books"
      parameters:
        - name: author
          in: query
          description: Author name filter
          allowEmptyValue: false
          required: true
          example: Josh Bloch
          schema:
            type: string
components:
  schemas:
    BookDto:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - name
        - author
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          description: Book unique ID
          readOnly: true
          example: 101
        name:
          type: string
          description: Book name
          readOnly: true
          example: Effective Java
        author:
          type: string
          description: Book author
          readOnly: true
          example: Josh Bloch
    Books:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: "#/components/schemas/BookDto"
